text: Tweigen dagas syndon on æghwilcum monðe, þæt swahwætswa man on þæm dagum onginneð, ne wurð hit næfre geendod.

Þæt is þonne: On Ianuarius, þonne se mona bið þreora nihta eald and feowra, and on Februarius, þonne he bið fifa and seofena eald, and on Martius þe syxta and se seofeða, on Aprilis se fifta and se eahteþa, and on Maius se eahteþa and se nygeþa, on Iunius seVand seXXVII, on Iulius seIIIand seXIII, on Agustus seVIIIand seXIII, on September seVand seIX, on October seVand seXV, on Nouember seVIIand seIX, on December se þridda and se þreotteoða.
Buton ælcan tweon, swa hit bið gewislice, gyme, seþe wille.
